✔ SOLID Principles 

Single Responsibility 

Open/Closed 

Liskov Substitution 

Interface Segregation 

Dependency Inversion 

✔ Other Essential Principles 

DRY 

KISS 

YAGNI 

GRASP principles (very important!) 

 

